@startuml
title UC04 - Cadastrar Empresa Parceira

' Configuração visual melhorada
hide footbox
autoactivate off
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #374151
    LifeLineBorderColor #9CA3AF
    LifeLineBackgroundColor #F9FAFB
    ParticipantBorderColor #374151
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #E8F5FF
    ActorBorderColor #374151
    ActorBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    DatabaseBorderColor #374151
    DatabaseBackgroundColor #F3E8FF
    BoxBorderColor #9CA3AF
    BoxBackgroundColor #FAFAFA
    GroupBorderColor #9CA3AF
    GroupBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    ActivationBorderColor #111827
    ActivationBackgroundColor #CFE3FF
    ParticipantPadding 28
    BoxPadding 10
    MessageAlign center
}
skinparam maxMessageSize 70

actor "Empresa Parceira" as E
boundary "Tela de Cadastro
Next.js" as Front
control "EmpresaController
Micronaut" as Ctrl
control "EmpresaRepository" as Repo
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

E -> Front: Preenche dados da empresa
activate Front
note right of Front
  Normaliza e-mail,
  remove máscara do CNPJ
  e valida campos.
end note

Front -> Ctrl: POST /empresas
EmpresaRequest
activate Ctrl
note right of Ctrl
  Valida dados obrigatórios
  e regras de unicidade.
end note

Ctrl -> Repo: save(empresa)
activate Repo
Repo -> DB: INSERT usuario/empresa
activate DB
DB --> Repo: Empresa salva
deactivate DB
Repo --> Ctrl: Empresa
deactivate Repo
Ctrl --> Front: 201 Created
EmpresaResponse
deactivate Ctrl
Front --> E: Exibe toast de sucesso
e atualiza lista
deactivate Front
@enduml
